[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ワン、ツー、ワン、ツー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00312",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "よし！　休憩にしまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00313",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ねぇ鬼門！　アタシのダンス、どうだった？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00314",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ものすごい成長を感じまする！\n数日前まで未経験だったとは思えませぬな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00315",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "やったー！　本番まであとちょっと、\nもっともっと上手になるぞー！　ぐんぐんハンマー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00316",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……ちょっと、イザナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00317",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ん？　どうしたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00318",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……１ｓｔライブの後、酷いこと言って悪かったわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00319",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あの時はあんたのこと、\nノリでアイドル始めた奴とか言ったけど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00320",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんたもあんたなりに頑張ってる姿を見て、\nちょっと考えを改めたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00321",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうヨハナー！\nアタシまだまだ下手くそだけど、一生懸命頑張るよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00322",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "頑張ってもらわなくちゃ困るわ。\n私たちは世界一のアイドルユニットになるんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00323",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そうでございますな。\n三人で頑張ってまいりましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00324",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ねえ二人とも。\nアイドルとしてのアタシの夢、聞いてくれる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00325",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アタシはね、大好きな友達――レスナちゃんに\n喜んでもらいたくてアイドルになろうと思ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00326",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "でも実際にアイドルやってみると、アタシも楽しくて、\nこの楽しさをたくさんの人に届けたいって思ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00327",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "だから！　アイドルとしてのアタシの夢は、\nレスナちゃんや世界中の人々を楽しませること！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00328",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あと、アタシ自身もアイドルを全力で楽しむこと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00329",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いい夢でござるな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00330",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者の夢は、忍術を用いた新しい楽しさを生み出し、\nファンの気持ちに応えることでございまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00331",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そして人気アイドルになって、\nお腹いっぱい食べられる生活をするのでござる～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00332",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "私の夢は、世界中の人々を魅了する\n世界一のアイドルになることよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00333",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "だって私にはそれができるだけの才能があるから。\n信じてくれている人の期待に応えたいから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00334",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "「できる」「できない」じゃなく、やってみせるわ。\nあんたたちと一緒にね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00335",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者らの夢、バラバラではございますが、\n人々を楽しませたいという想いは同じでござるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00336",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　改めて一致団結！\n２ｎｄライブも頑張ろう！　ハンマー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00337",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ハンマー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00338",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……何よその掛け声。嫌よ、私はやらないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00339",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "えーっ！　ヨハナも一緒にハンマーしようよ！\nアタシのハンマー貸してあげる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00340",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ちょっ！　いらないっつーの！　ハンマーバカ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00341",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "雨降ってハンマーで地固まったようですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00342",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ、２ｎｄライブが楽しみですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00343",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]